Ranger Help for: carve bow
===========================

SYNTAX:      make bow
             make shortbow
             make longbow
             make crossbow
             carve bow
             carve shortbow
             carve longbow
             carve crossbow
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   7
BASE SP:     70
SKILL TYPE:  archery

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to craft one of three temporary ranged
weapons from wood: shortbow, longbow, or crossbow. The quality of the
bow depends on the Ranger's wilderness training and mental/physical
crafting ability.

Shortbows are suited to fast archery and furyfire. Longbows are suited
to longfire. Crossbows are slower, hit harder, use bolts, and are
required for heartshot.
